title: Reading with Randos: The Sickness Unto Death (Part 1)
description:
Another set of Randos kicks off a new reading, Søren Kierkegaard's "The Sickness Unto Death."  Enjoy this first in a series of readings and reflections.

Join the ConverZation here:
https://discord.gg/j8ps92H

Check out Paul Vanderklay's channel here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGsD...
https://medium.com/@kcsycamore/saccad...
